data.value: # Choose three points on the given x-y plane to create a Triangle. # Please note that only 3 points can be chosen on the x-y plane. # Press RESET to return to the initial state. # You can either ZOOM IN or ZOOM OUT by choosing the size in the zoom section. # Have fun using our Triangle Drawer. # Developed by: Lương Vỹ Đạt Nguyễn Cao Nhân Nguyễn Đào Đức Quân
